{"uuid": "6dcba6ea-25e9-4898-a510-bf3a8022e201", "id": 55237, "date": "2024-12-04T04:00:10", "date_gmt": "2024-12-04T12:00:10", "guid": {"rendered": "https://estreetshuffle.com/?p=55237"}, "modified": "2024-11-27T14:06:23", "modified_gmt": "2024-11-27T22:06:23", "slug": "kingdom-of-days-december-4", "status": "publish", "type": "post", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2024/12/04/kingdom-of-days-december-4/", "title": {"rendered": "Kingdom of Days: December 4"}, "content": {"rendered": "<p><em><strong>New for 2024:\u00a0</strong>New entry for 2023</em></p>\n<p><strong>1948: </strong>Bruce&#8217;s good friend, frequent co-performer, and one-time bandmate Southside Johnny Lyon is born in Neptune, New Jersey.</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"14495\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/southside/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/southside.jpg?fit=600%2C603&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"600,603\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"southside\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/southside.jpg?fit=300%2C300&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/southside.jpg?fit=600%2C603&amp;ssl=1\" class=\" wp-image-14495 aligncenter\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/southside-300x300.jpg?resize=758%2C758\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"758\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/southside.jpg?resize=300%2C300&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/southside.jpg?resize=150%2C150&amp;ssl=1 150w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/southside.jpg?resize=550%2C550&amp;ssl=1 550w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/southside.jpg?resize=600%2C600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/southside.jpg?resize=50%2C50&amp;ssl=1 50w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1971:\u00a0</strong>The Bruce Springsteen Band is in residence at the Student Prince in Asbury Park.</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"23010\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1971-12-04/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/1971-12-04.png?fit=977%2C464&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"977,464\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1971-12-04\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/1971-12-04.png?fit=300%2C142&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/1971-12-04.png?fit=758%2C360&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-23010\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/1971-12-04.png?resize=758%2C359&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"359\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/1971-12-04.png?resize=300%2C142&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/1971-12-04.png?resize=768%2C365&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/1971-12-04.png?w=977&amp;ssl=1 977w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1980:\u00a0</strong>At their River Tour stop at the Buffalo Memorial Auditorium, Bruce and the E Street Band tour premiere &#8220;<a href=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2022/04/01/matr-bruce-springsteen-and-don-henley-i-fought-the-law/\">I Fought the Law</a>&#8221; and officially usher in the holiday season with their first &#8220;<a href=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2021/12/24/cover-me-santa-claus-is-comin-to-town/\">Santa Claus is Comin&#8217; to Town</a>&#8221; of the tour. Check out rare video footage of a couple of songs.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Bruce Springsteen - Buffalo 1980 Muchmusic footage\" width=\"758\" height=\"569\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/PGnzoL3by14?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen></iframe></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"14496\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/40492702103_734e8a51f0_o/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/40492702103_734e8a51f0_o.jpg?fit=728%2C1200&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"728,1200\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"40492702103_734e8a51f0_o\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/40492702103_734e8a51f0_o.jpg?fit=182%2C300&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/40492702103_734e8a51f0_o.jpg?fit=621%2C1024&amp;ssl=1\" class=\" wp-image-14496 aligncenter\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/40492702103_734e8a51f0_o-182x300.jpg?resize=758%2C1249\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"1249\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/40492702103_734e8a51f0_o.jpg?resize=182%2C300&amp;ssl=1 182w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/40492702103_734e8a51f0_o.jpg?resize=621%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 621w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/40492702103_734e8a51f0_o.jpg?w=728&amp;ssl=1 728w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1990:\u00a0</strong>Bruce records &#8220;<a href=\"http://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2018/10/24/roll-of-the-dice-my-lover-man/\">My Lover Man</a>&#8221; at Soundworks West in Los Angeles.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"My Lover Man (Studio Outtake - 1990)\" width=\"758\" height=\"569\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/n-jzr3jSDX0?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen></iframe></div>\n<p><strong>1999:\u00a0</strong>The Diasco family gets an unexpected Christmas bonus: in June, they&#8217;d bid on and won a private Bon Jovi performance at their home in an auction benefiting the Doug Flutie Autism Foundation; when the band shows up to honor their obligation, they bring along some friends: Bruce, Patti, and Southside Johnny. Bruce joins Bon Jovi for six songs.</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"23011\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1999-12-04/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/1999-12-04.png?fit=454%2C898&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"454,898\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1999-12-04\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/1999-12-04.png?fit=152%2C300&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/1999-12-04.png?fit=454%2C898&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-23011\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/1999-12-04.png?resize=758%2C1496&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"1496\" /></p>\n<p><strong>2001:\u00a0</strong>Bruce, The Max Weinberg 7 and a host of friends play their second of five holiday shows at Asbury Park&#8217;s Convention Hall in support of local charities. All of last night&#8217;s guests are present, plus The Miami Horns, who kick things off with &#8220;Deck the Halls,&#8221; followed by &#8220;<a href=\"http://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2019/03/14/roll-of-the-dice-wild-billys-circus-story/\">Wild Billy&#8217;s Circus Story</a>&#8221; played by just Bruce and Garry (on tuba).</p>\n<div id=\"v-K55rhq4Y-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/K55rhq4Y?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><strong>2002:\u00a0</strong>The Rising Tour stops at Mellon Arena in Pittsburgh, where Joe Grushecky joins Bruce for the tour premiere of &#8220;<a href=\"http://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2018/08/27/codeofsilence/\">Code of Silence</a>&#8221; and stays through &#8220;<a href=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2024/06/04/roll-of-the-dice-glory-days/\">Glory Days</a>&#8221; and &#8220;Born to Run.&#8221; Bruce also tour premieres &#8220;<a href=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2023/05/01/roll-of-the-dice-youngstown/\">Youngstown</a>&#8221; and the show-closing &#8220;Santa Claus is Comin&#8217; to Town.&#8221;</p>\n<div id=\"v-fMgCtazQ-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='568' src='https://videopress.com/embed/fMgCtazQ?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"23012\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/2002-12-04/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/2002-12-04.png?fit=2076%2C1055&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"2076,1055\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"2002-12-04\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/2002-12-04.png?fit=300%2C152&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/2002-12-04.png?fit=758%2C385&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-23012\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/2002-12-04.png?resize=758%2C384&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"384\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/2002-12-04.png?resize=300%2C152&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/2002-12-04.png?resize=1024%2C520&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/2002-12-04.png?resize=768%2C390&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>2007:\u00a0</strong>The Magic Tour heads north to Scandinavia, starting with a show at the Oslo Spektrum.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Springsteen, Oslo Spectrum 04 December 2007. Santa claus\" width=\"758\" height=\"569\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/T6s2T96l35A?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen></iframe></div>\n<p><strong>2012:\u00a0</strong>Bruce kicks off his last week of the American Wrecking Ball Tour with a show at the Honda Center in Anaheim. Tom Morello joins the band for seven songs, including the show opener and closer, and Mike Ness makes a guest appearance as well for the tour premiere of &#8220;<a href=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2020/06/25/matr-bruce-springsteen-and-mike-ness-bad-luck/\">Bad Luck</a>.&#8221; &#8220;<a href=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2022/06/19/roll-of-the-dice-long-time-comin/\">Long Time Comin&#8217;</a>&#8221; also makes its tour debut at this show.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Bruce Springsteen &quot; Land of Hope and Dreams&quot; Anaheim 12-4-12\" width=\"758\" height=\"426\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/JKvcjZepxjg?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen></iframe></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Bruce Springsteen &quot;Spirit in the Night&quot; Anaheim 12-4-12\" width=\"758\" height=\"426\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/IO_uSc0RacQ?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen></iframe></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Long Time Coming - Bruce Springsteen - Anaheim, CA - 12/4/12\" width=\"758\" height=\"426\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/a84H2zWxixs?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen></iframe></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Bruce Sp